import React from 'react'
import { Card, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

export default function TitleGridItem() {
    return (
        <Card style={{ width: '12rem', height: '14rem' }}>
            <Card.Img variant="top" src="holder.js/100px180" />
            <Card.Body>
                <Card.Title style={{ fontFamily: 'Open Sans', fontWeight: '600' }}>Card Title</Card.Title>
                <Card.Text style={{ fontFamily: 'Open Sans', fontWeight: '300', marginTop: '-10px' }}>
                    Fantasy/Drama
                </Card.Text>
            </Card.Body>
        </Card>
    )
}
